meowiitten 2025-07-10 01:24 a.m.
Under this case, I am presenting two theories of liability for libel: one is for defamation per se, the other is for defamation by implication. Count two is alternatively plead to count one. You can pick which theory of liability if you find that the defendant is, in fact, liable for the statements he made.

For defamation per se, I need not show specific damages. Harm is presumed since the statements are particularly offensive and targeted. In the alternative, defamation by implication is proven regardless because, even if any statement was possibly true, they were still defamatory and exposed me to ridicule or had a tendency to injure my reputation.

As a baseline, under 5 M.S.C. 1 3104.1, a person is liable for libel if spread something in text that (2) "exposes any person to hatred, contempt, ridicule, or obloquy," or (2) "which causes him to be shunned or avoided," or (3) "which has a tendency to injure him in his occupation[.]" If you find that any of those three elements are satisfied, or any combination, then you must find him liable. The easiest is the third since it only requires a tendency to harm.

To quote the statements in question from the defendant, which were made in my public marketplace channel (for my legal organization, the Columbian Alliance for Equal Rights in the Clark County main discord, they are as follows, and in order:

"Didnt listen to my story and simply removed me from the server and closed the ticket. I guess even the anti discrimination people discriminate against criminals."

"Yeah this cocksucker saodimpacto (thats also known for falsely arresting people through contempt of court) basically removed me from his shitty non profit after I told him how I was discriminated against for being a violent criminal and being denied an expungement."

A lot of people saw these in the channel, and as you can see in the Exhibit attached to the complaint, they began egging the defendant on to continue making those claims about me and my organization. It also drew unwanted attention to my forum page and I had to delete that since it just became a shitshow because of what he started.

The false claims are as follows: (1) that I falsely arrest people (I can't even arrest people); (2) I operate a fraudulent non-profit (we are registered with the state); and (3) I am cocksucker (I am heterosexual).
